title: DoctorStory1
tags:
position: 169,38
---
Doctor Ghost: You know, this cute little cafe reminds me of the coffee shop near the medical school I attended.
<<emotionChange Happy Flowers>>
Doctor Ghost: The barista there always had a huge smile on her face as she made everyone's orders. She messed up a few times, but she always tried her best.
Doctor Ghost: Her enthusiasm was simply infectious- pun not intended.
<<emotionChange Normal>>
Doctor Ghost: It always amazes me how much actions can change another person's life.
<<emotionChange Concern>>
Doctor Ghost: As a doctor, I've treated so many patients. Some of them were old, barely hanging on to life. Still, they fought to stay with their loved ones as long as possible.
Doctor Ghost: Others were young, hurt by things out of their control. People of all ages and backgrounds all come to the hospital for the same purpose: another chance at life.
<<emotionChange Normal>>
Doctor Ghost: Whenever I see their smile or the smile of their loved ones, I realize how much I changed their lives.
Doctor Ghost: When I was young, I never could have imagined what direction my life would go. But it was all thanks to a stranger that I became who I am today.
Doctor Ghost: I hope I can find them one day, so I can thank them.
<<emotionChange Happy Flowers>>
Doctor Ghost: Keep up the good work. I'm sure it will all pay off one day.
<<emotionChange Normal>>
<<setCam "Main Camera">>
===

title: DoctorStory2
