<<emotionChange Concern>>
Doctor Ghost: Hey... Have you seen...? Never mind.
Doctor Ghost: This shouldn't be something I should bother you with. If you wish to know, however, I'm looking for a certain soldier.
<<emotionChange Normal>>
Doctor Ghost: He was the stranger I mentioned last time. I heard from some other ghosts that he might have been here.
Doctor Ghost: I... I have to find him.
Doctor Ghost: He was the reason why I lived to become a doctor.
Doctor Ghost: Why I... even had the chance to live in the first place.
<<emotionChange Concern>>
Doctor Ghost: I contracted a debilitating illness when I was young. And because our village didn't have a doctor, I was certain I was going to die.
Doctor Ghost: A group of doctors from a neighboring town was dispatched to provide aid, but some bandits saw this as an opportunity to steal supplies and attacked our village. That soldier saved me... at the cost of his own life.
Doctor Ghost: I didn't want his sacrifice to be in vain, so I pushed myself to live.
<<emotionChange Normal>>
Doctor Ghost: When the aid arrived, I dedicated myself to become a doctor as well.
<<setCam "Main Camera">>
